        {
          "orderIndex": 2,
          "blockType": "rich_text",
          "title": null,
          "data": {
            "html": "<ul><li>Patient's are much more than their diagnosis</li><li>The patient's perceived needs and concerns</li><li>The patient's understanding of their current situation</li><li>Can the patient identify influences on their current health concerns/crisis?</li><li>Patient's perceived barriers to care and overall SCD management</li><li>Do they have access to primary and comprehensive care?</li><li>What does their personal support system look like?</li><li>Patient's perspective on the most appropriate intervention and their supportive needs</li><li>It is important to support and validate patient's willingness to reach out for support, as well as their current situation</li></ul>",
            "gridX": 0, "gridY": 6, "gridW": 12, "gridH": 4
          }
        },
