    {
      "orderIndex": 2,
      "slideType": "content",
      "title": "Questions to Consider",
      "settings": { "background": "#FFFFFF", "block_style": "glass" },
      "blocks": [
        {
          "orderIndex": 0,
          "blockType": "rich_text",
          "title": null,
          "data": {
            "html": "<p><strong>Reducing Disparities in Care</strong> Consider the disparity in healthcare access among the SCD population and how you can help to mitigate that disparity.</p><ul><li>Check your biases</li><li>Validate the patient's experience</li><li>Consider how you can role model care that seeks to educate, empower, and encourage patients in their disease management.</li><li>Intervene where there are blocks/barriers; being willing to extend scope of advocacy beyond your role.</li><li>Understand the barriers that exist in healthcare.</li></ul>",
            "gridX": 0, "gridY": 0, "gridW": 12, "gridH": 4
          }
        },
        {
          "orderIndex": 1,
          "blockType": "rich_text",
          "title": null,
          "data": {
            "html": "<p><strong>Reflect on your role in educating, empowering, and encouraging patients in their disease management. How can you role model care that seeks to achieve these goals?</strong></p>",
            "gridX": 0, "gridY": 4, "gridW": 12, "gridH": 2
          }
        },
